interesting points: The object was white in color and appeared on the radar scope before fading out., The observation lasted for about 7 minutes., Multiple conclusions were drawn including balloon and aircraft, but the data was deemed insufficient for final evaluation., The report is part of the U.S. Air Force's Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings., Additional details mention a bright light noticed at various locations.
